text:
5 Days, 5 Ways: Celebs Can't Get Enough of These Head-to-Toe Black Outfits for Fall 
E online Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Who said that black has to be boring?Blame it on the upcoming holiday season, or perhaps just on our affinity for all things dark and mysterious. If you ask us, you can never be wearing too much of the dark shade. Fashion girls are notorious for stocking up on the staple color, and for good reason. For one, the hue is ultra-slimming and it's difficult to not feel your best when wearing it. While there's really no way to go wrong with the safe-but-daring color, we're currently inspired by the news ways that celebs are making it fresh again for fall.
